'''K·J·麦克丹尼尔斯'''（{{lang-en|'''K.J. McDaniels'''}}，{{bd|1993年|2月9日|}}）為美国职业[[篮球运动员|篮球运动员]]。出生于[[亚拉巴马州|亚拉巴马州]][[伯明翰_(亚拉巴马州)|伯明翰]]，大学时期他效力于[[克莱门森大学|克莱门森大学]]。

==大学生涯==
麦克丹尼尔斯高中就读于中心公园基督学院，在此期间他只是个无名小卒<ref name=Overlooked>{{cite news|last1=Herbert|first1=James|title=2014 NBA Draft: K.J. McDaniels, overlooked as usual|url=http://www.cbssports.com/nba/eye-on-basketball/24595968/nba-draft-kj-mcdaniels-overlooked-as-usual|accessdate=2014-06-27|publisher=CBS Sports|date=2014-06-24|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303224818/http://www.cbssports.com/nba/eye-on-basketball/24595968/nba-draft-kj-mcdaniels-overlooked-as-usual|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在他的大学联赛新人赛季只有极为有限的出场时间，场均贡献3.9分1.8个[[篮板球|篮板球]]<ref name="clemsonbio">{{cite web|title=#32 K.J. McDaniels|url=http://www.clemsontigers.com/ViewArticle.dbml?DB_OEM_ID=28500&ATCLID=205528955|accessdate=2014-12-12|publisher=CBS Sports|date=2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161225181659/http://www.clemsontigers.com/ViewArticle.dbml?DB_OEM_ID=28500&ATCLID=205528955|archive-date=2016-12-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在他的二年级赛季，他成为克莱门森阵中更重要的人物，在这个赛季他场均得分和篮板球均有大幅上涨，得分和篮板球数据分别为10.9分和5个篮板球，此外，他还有2.1个[[封盖|封盖]]，这个数据可以在ACC联盟里排名次席<ref name="clemsonbio"/><ref>{{cite web | last =  | first =  | title = K. J. McDaniels CBSSports.com profile | work = CBSSports.com | date =  | url = http://www.cbssports.com/collegebasketball/players/playerpage/1904213/kj-mcdaniels | accessdate = 2014-05-04 | archive-date = 2016-12-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161231124218/http://www.cbssports.com/collegebasketball/players/playerpage/1904213/kj-mcdaniels }}</ref>。在他的大三赛季，麦克丹尼尔斯成为了他所在的ACC联盟中的顶尖球员。他场均可以砍下17.1分，7.1个篮板球，外加2。8次封盖，封盖数为全联盟之冠。赛季结束后，麦克丹尼尔斯获得了该联盟最佳防守球员称号，并进入了最佳阵容第一队<ref>{{cite web | last =  | first =  | title = Clemson's McDaniels named ACC defensive player of the year | work = GoUpstate.com | date = 2014-03-11 | url = http://www.goupstate.com/article/20140311/ARTICLES/140319921 | accessdate = 2014-05-04 | archive-date = 2016-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160809002439/http://www.goupstate.com/article/20140311/ARTICLES/140319921 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在他的带领下，克莱门森大学获得了NCAA全国邀请赛的资格，并成功得到了在[[麦迪逊广场花园|麦迪逊广场花园]]进行半决赛的机会<ref>{{cite web | last =  | first =  | title = Clemson rallies past Belmont, advances to NIT semifinals | work = [[CBSSports.com|CBSSports.com]] | date = 2014-03-25 | url = http://www.cbssports.com/collegebasketball/gametracker/recap/NCAAB_20140325_BELMONT@CLEM | accessdate = 2014-05-04 | archive-date = 2016-12-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161231124607/http://www.cbssports.com/collegebasketball/gametracker/recap/NCAAB_20140325_BELMONT@CLEM | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==NBA生涯==
2014年4月4日，麦克丹尼尔斯宣布放弃最后一年的大学学业，参加当年的[[NBA选秀|NBA选秀]]<ref>{{cite web | last = Feldman | first = Dan | title = Report: Clemson’s K.J. McDaniels to declare for NBA draft | work = [[NBCSports.com|NBCSports.com]] | date = 2014-04-22 | url = http://probasketballtalk.nbcsports.com/2014/04/22/report-clemsons-k-j-mcdaniels-to-declare-for-nba-draft/ | accessdate = 2014-12-12 | archive-date = 2014-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141101153239/http://probasketballtalk.nbcsports.com/2014/04/22/report-clemsons-k-j-mcdaniels-to-declare-for-nba-draft/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2014年6月26日的[[2014年NBA選秀|2014年NBA選秀]]中，麦克丹尼尔斯被[[费城76人|费城76人]]以总第32顺位选择<ref>{{cite news|title=Sixers Select McDaniels, Grant, Micic in the Second Round of the 2014 NBA Draft|url=http://www.nba.com/sixers/news/140626-second-round|accessdate=2014-12-12|work=NBA.com|date=2014-12-12|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114004000/https://www.nba.com/sixers/news/140626-second-round|dead-url=no}}</ref>。随后，他代表76人队出战了同年的[[NBA夏季联赛|NBA夏季联赛]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Rappaport|first=Max|title=Orlando Pro Summer League: Schedule And Roster|url=http://www.nba.com/sixers/news/140704-opsl-schedule-roster|accessdate=2014-07-07|work=NBA.com|date=2014-07-04|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121041149/https://www.nba.com/sixers/news/140704-opsl-schedule-roster|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年9月29日，麦克丹尼尔斯进入了76人的训练营名单<ref>{{cite news|title=Sixers Announce 2014 Training Camp Roster|url=http://www.nba.com/sixers/news/140929-camp-roster|accessdate=2014-10-01|work=NBA.com|date=2014-09-29|archive-date=2017-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808075319/http://www.nba.com/sixers/news/140929-camp-roster/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月1日，麦克丹尼尔斯与费城76人签订了一份为期一年的合同，这使得他会在下一年夏天成为一名完全自由球员<ref>{{cite news|last=Wojnarowski|first=Adrian|title=Philadelphia's K.J. McDaniels takes bold approach to rookie deal|url=https://sports.yahoo.com/news/philadelphia-s-k-j--mcdaniels-takes-bold-approach-to-rookie-deal-143327281.html|accessdate=2014-10-01|work=Yahoo.com|date=2014-10-01|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015116/http://sports.yahoo.com/news/philadelphia-s-k-j--mcdaniels-takes-bold-approach-to-rookie-deal-143327281.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

